          The Best Free Day Trading Simulator Online
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)] text-[16px] leading-relaxed mb-6">
          As a <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">free day trading simulator</strong>, Stockade gives you two distinct environments. The <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">live simulator</strong> streams six assets simultaneously with 800ms price ticks, letting you practice reacting to fast-moving markets in real time. The historical simulator lets you replay entire trading sessions candle-by-candle at your own pace — perfect for building pattern recognition without the pressure of a live market. Unlike broker-based <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">paper trading simulators</strong> that require registration and link to real accounts, Stockade works instantly, anonymously, and completely free — making it the top choice for a <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">fake day trading simulator</strong> experience that mirrors the real thing.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[var(--c-text)] mb-3 mt-8">
          Multi-Asset Trading: Stocks, Crypto, Forex & Futures
        </h3>
        <p class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)] text-[16px] leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Stockade is a truly multi-asset <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">virtual stock market simulator</strong>. Trade 14 equity tickers with realistic price behavior, practice volatile BTC and ETH moves on the <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">crypto trading simulator</strong>, develop discipline on major and minor currency pairs with the built-in <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">forex trading simulator</strong>, or stress-test strategies on NQ, ES, CL, and GC contracts using the <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">futures trading simulator</strong>. One platform. Every market. All free.
