          Stockade is the ideal <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">stock market simulator for students</strong>. It requires zero installation, zero account creation, and zero budget — which makes it the go-to <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">free stock market simulator for students</strong> in high school economics classes, university finance courses, and trading clubs worldwide. Teachers can run paper trading competitions and have students analyze their results through the built-in analytics dashboard: equity curve, win rate, profit factor, average win/loss, maximum drawdown, and a time-of-day heatmap that shows when trades perform best.
