        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6 ml-4">
          {[
            'Real candlestick charts with volume',
            'Professional indicators: EMA, VWAP, RSI, MACD',
            'Full order panel: market, limit, stop-loss, take-profit, OCO',
            'Performance analytics with equity curves and drawdown tracking',
            'Complete mobile and tablet support',
          ].map(item => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 text-[15px] text-[var(--c-text-muted)]">
              <span class="text-[#22c55e] mt-0.5 shrink-0">✓</span>
              <span>{item}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <p class="text-[var(--c-text-muted)] text-[16px] leading-relaxed">
          No trials. No freemium tiers. No upsells. Stockade is the most complete <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">free trading simulator</strong> on the web — a professional <strong class="text-[var(--c-text)]">stock market simulator &amp; game</strong> that takes trading education as seriously as you do. Launch the simulator and build your edge.
